     C* B4: alphameric look-ahead fields must 9-fill at EOF (83344-46),
     C* not stay unchanged. LADATA2 has 2 records: '10','20'. On the
     C* last record (CUR2=20) the look-ahead NALA must read '99'.
     FLADATA2 IP  F    2               DISK
     ILADATA2     AA
     I                                        1   2 CUR2
     I            **
     I                                        1   2 NALA
     C           CUR2      COMP '20'                     20
     C  20       NALA      COMP '99'                     21
     C  21                 Z-ADD1         RPGRET
